Restitution Summary

Defendant Rollie M Tappa in court, in custody, with attorney Kirk A Redetzke.   Pablo Galaviz appeared for the State of Wisconsin. Amended Information filed - reading waived.   Defendant enters a plea of no contest to Counts 1 and 2,  Court finds defendant guilty.

Court orders the following: 
Ct. 1:
- 9 months jail straight time concurrent to Ct. 2 but consecutive to prison STAYED for 2 years Probation - concurrent to Ct. 2
- Court costs of $253.00 (includes DRGOD) to be paid as a Condition of Probation; alternate 6 days jail - consecutive
- Restitution of $20,208.00 to be paid joint and severally with co-actors to Barbara S. ($16,600) and Liberty Mutual Ins. Co. ($3608).
- Conditions of Probation: Maintain absolute sobriety. No contact with the victims whatsoever.  DNA  surcharge is waived.

Ct. 2:
- 9 months jail straight time concurrent to Ct. 1 but consecutive to prison STAYED for 2 years Probation - concurrent to Ct. 1
- Court costs of $243.00 to be paid as a Condition of Probation; alternate 5 days jail - consecutive
- Conditions of Probation: Maintain absolute sobriety. No contact with the victims whatsoever.  DNA  surcharge is waived.
Plea/sentencing hearing on May 7, 2014 at 08:30 am.
